## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the search. Some sources may not reflect the most current data or perspectives, and the analysis is constrained by the information accessible through the selected databases. Additionally, the complexity of racism as a social construct means that interpretations and definitions can vary, potentially affecting the conclusions drawn in this report.